posts.message:
Anybody interested in spending a few days at Dahab, geeking by day and chilling by night ?

This would include technical sessions and discussions, about hottest trends, being a good developer, living the digital nomad life, and probably a shot at a simple product by the group.

Pricing would range from 1k to 2k per a week, and maybe less for groups, it would be the last week of August starting at Thursday 25 August, so we get a chance to chill before school ( for parents and students ), and go on for a week. People can spend as much days as possible though.

This is a free thing, you pay for what you take, not an ad for a travel agency.

Who's interested ?
